> *"Built an end-to-end smart city analytics platform processing Singapore's 87 national LTA traffic cameras: fine-tuned YOLOv11 (92% mAP, INT8 quantized), BoT-SORT tracking, spatial-temporal congestion prediction fusing weather/taxi/air quality data, autoencoder anomaly detection with 6-category failure analysis, and statistical drift monitoring — published as an open multi-modal traffic dataset on Kaggle."*
